title: FIJI MISSION IN NEW YORK CELEBRATES FIJI DAY (Government of the Republic of Fiji)
text: ( Source : Government of the Republic of Fiji ) 10/11/ 2015 Fiji Day was celebrated in New York today at a luncheon attended by one hundred diplomats of the United Nations . The diplomatic luncheon was hosted by the Permanent Mission of Fiji to
